### scripts/gen-status.sh (source of truth: git + docs/issues/_events.jsonl).
docs-site/docs/slice-status.md

### Slice 069 — Playwright runner artifacts
web/playwright-report/
web/test-results/

### Slice 178 — UI honesty audit harness raw reports.
### The harness writes per-run JSON / markdown / screenshots under
### web/e2e-audit/reports/. Seeded-stack runs upload the directory as a
### CI artifact (informational job); the curated first-pass summary is
### committed separately at docs/audit-log/178-ui-honesty-first-pass.md.
### Operator-local prod runs (PLATFORM_BASE_URL override) write under
### web/e2e-audit/reports/local-prod/ which is double-locked to never
### be committed (P0-178-3 — real-tenant data must not leak).
web/e2e-audit/reports/

### Slice 057 — README capture pipeline bundled artifact
web/scripts/.capture-readme-screenshots.bundled.js
